{"tid":282309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯議員嘲餐廳變水舞間 網民轟幸災樂禍","createTime":"2017-06-13T09:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T10:27:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"017f720919be3a03de88281d20153ad9324f7c73","tid":282309,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170613/large/1497338887_6b2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170613%2Flarge%2F1497338887_6b2d.png&h=e603699f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅雨下本港多處水浸，其中中環卑路乍街茶餐廳「美食廊」水浸入舖，民建聯中西區區議員陳學鋒早上在facebook上載相片，形容餐廳變成「水舞間」，並配有從容自若的表情符號，反問「點樣喺『水舞間』食早餐而又不失霸氣？」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民留言批評陳欠同情心，「人哋間舖搞成咁，好好笑咩？」、「身為區議員，唔去慰問、協助小店人員搵出問題所在，仲喺度幸災樂禍，水舞間你都講得出，如果你屋企水浸，畀人話水舞間，你覺得好funny（有趣）？」<br />\n<br />\n【網民點睇】<br />\n<br />\nNicole Wong：人哋間舖搞成咁，好好笑咩？人無恥便無敵！<br />\n<br />\nRocena Lee Yan Yan：證明陳學鋒你無同理心、同情心，你真係無恥！影衰晒堅摩區！身為區議員，唔去慰問、協助小店人員搵出問題所在，仲喺度幸災樂禍，水舞間你都講得出，如果你屋企水浸，畀人話水舞間，你覺得好funny？你個腦是咪畀水浸壞咗？<br />\n<br />\nAndy Pui Yee Hong：一啲都唔好笑；入得民賤聯嘅，已經放棄做人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170613/large/1497338823_d3d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170613%2Flarge%2F1497338823_d3d1.jpg&h=e39a9d41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10515f75167859f7d6dc0653d38fbb77a9801fe6","tid":282309,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:15:52.000Z","msg":"on 9"},{"pid":"e1db449f32351111bf4ee15faa435c79930f89ac","tid":282309,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"以為自己好好笑"},{"pid":"143109058308f0aca9819abb8079677e375d3e92","tid":282309,"uid":113163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:23:54.000Z","msg":"上一次九龍灣火燭咪又有民建聯嘅人嚟影相 根本就係臭罌出臭草"},{"pid":"b671a421dfe711a1b1a7f8e39b8a196c78f1524d","tid":282309,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:25:58.000Z","msg":"陳學鋒我失你老味咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5155755efb4960f449bf568da17eff60090651","tid":282309,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T09:27:40.000Z","msg":"咁都算水舞間? 屌你真係一來戇鳩二來柒三來白撚痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13db567170e7055dd9b2b891880978f92f527763","tid":282309,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"點樣好似陳學峰咁戇鳩而又不失霸氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}